@Component public class YahooSplitCalendar extends AbstractYahooFinanceConnector implements ISplitCalendarFeedConnector
Yahoo Split Calendar implementation using the new POST API and base connector class. Extends AbstractYahooFinanceConnector to leverage common Yahoo Finance API functionality.
